Text: condolencesplease accept our condolences for the loss of you father The Governor and I put family first and in this time our hearts and thoughts are with you as a son We look forward to meeting with you at another time Paul did a great job and we thank ENRON for having a good strategy and good people to manage it Stephen Reynolds
